  <!-- EN: Spirit beasts join -->
  <RI_AnimalCome.label>灵兽加入</RI_AnimalCome.label>
  <!-- EN: Spirit beasts join -->
  <RI_AnimalCome.letterLabel>灵兽加入</RI_AnimalCome.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A group of spiritual beasts, influenced by the changes in spiritual energy, became friendly and voluntarily joined the colony. -->
  <RI_AnimalCome.letterText>一群灵兽被灵气所影响，变得亲人，主动加入了你的殖民地。</RI_AnimalCome.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Spirit beasts pass -->
  <RI_AnimalMigration.label>灵兽路过</RI_AnimalMigration.label>
  <!-- EN: Spirit beasts pass -->
  <RI_AnimalMigration.letterLabel>灵兽路过</RI_AnimalMigration.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A group of spiritual beasts were attracted by the Qi and came pass your colony. -->
  <RI_AnimalMigration.letterText>一群灵兽被灵气所影响，改变了迁徙路线，路过你的殖民地。</RI_AnimalMigration.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Cultivator fall to earth -->
  <RI_DropEnergyStone.label>修士陨落</RI_DropEnergyStone.label>
  <!-- EN: Immortal fall -->
  <RI_DropEnergyStone.letterLabel>修士陨落</RI_DropEnergyStone.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A glowing figure streaks across the sky from a distance and explodes in midair. His remains landed impartially near your colony. -->
  <RI_DropEnergyStone.letterText>一道散发着光芒的人影从远处划过天际，在空中发生了爆炸。他的遗骸不偏不倚地落到了你的殖民地附近。</RI_DropEnergyStone.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Qi tide flood period -->
