  <!-- EN: A group of spiritual beasts that went crazy for no reason, attracted by the spiritual energy, charged into your colony! -->
  <RI_FrenziedAnimal.letterText>一群不知为何而发狂的灵兽，被灵气所吸引，冲向你的殖民地！</RI_FrenziedAnimal.letterText>
  
