  <RI_Incident_QingMing.letterLabel>青冥树生长</RI_Incident_QingMing.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: 青冥树自然生长。 -->
  <RI_Incident_QingMing.letterText>受到灵气波动影响，稀有的青冥树苗破土而出。</RI_Incident_QingMing.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Herbs sprout -->
  <RI_Incident_Sprout.label>药草萌芽</RI_Incident_Sprout.label>
  <!-- EN: Herbs sprout -->
  <RI_Incident_Sprout.letterLabel>药草萌芽</RI_Incident_Sprout.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Feel the nourishment of Crystal Vein Soil as several rare herbs awaken from dormancy and begin to grow. -->
  <RI_Incident_Sprout.letterText>感受到灵土的滋养，几种罕见的药草从休眠中苏醒并开始生长。</RI_Incident_Sprout.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Crystal vein recovery -->
  <RI_MakeLINGMAI.label>灵脉复苏</RI_MakeLINGMAI.label>
  <!-- EN: Crystal vein recovery -->
  <RI_MakeLINGMAI.letterLabel>灵脉复苏</RI_MakeLINGMAI.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A Crystal Vein has been revived, the earth radiates a strange light and a constant flow of energy is nourishing the soil from below, herbs can only grow on this spiritual soil. -->
  <RI_MakeLINGMAI.letterText>一处灵脉复苏了，大地散发出奇异的光芒，源源不断的能量正从地下滋养着泥土，野生药材只能在这种灵土上生长。</RI_MakeLINGMAI.letterText>
  
